<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[صارة]</span>: اسم موضع <span class="c2">«٤»</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>... همزة<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[الصاءة]</span>،<span class="c5"> مهموز:</span> الماء الذي يكون في السَّلَى <span class="c2">«٥»</span>.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
